    "arv27:90": "lāñchana-pāṇi-pāda-talāś-ca Buddhā Bhagavanto bhavanti ||",
    "arv27:91": "Imāny-aśītir-anuvyañjanāni ||",
    "arv27:92": "Conclusion",
    "arv27:93": "Yad-uktaṁ Bhagavatā:",
    "arv27:94": "“Dharmaṁ vo bhikṣavo deśayiṣyāmi ādau kalyāṇaṁ madhye kalyāṇaṁ paryavasāne kalyāṇaṁ | svarthaṁ savyañjanam | kevalaṁ paripurṇaṁ parisuddhaṁ paryavadātaṁ brahmacaryaṁ saṁprakāśayiṣye | yad-uta, Artha-Viniścayaṁ nāma Dharma-paryāyam.”-iti",
    "arv27:95": "Me yad-uktam-idaṁ tat-pratyuktam:",
    "arv27:96": "“Etāni vo bhikṣavo ’raṇyāyatanāni vṛkṣa-mūlāni śūnyāgārāṇi | parvata-kandara-giriguhā-palāla-puñjāni | abhyavakāśa-śmaśāna-vana-prastha-pantāni | śayanāsanāni adhyāvasat ||",
    "arv27:97": "Dhyāyat, bhikṣavo, mā pramādyat | mā paścād-vipratisāriṇo bhaviṣyatha.”",
    "arv27:98": "Idam-anuśāsanam ||",
    "arv27:99": "Asmin khalu punar-Dharma-paryāye bhāṣyamāṇe pañcānāṁ bhikṣu-śatānām-anupādāyāsravebhyaś-cittāni vimuktāni ||",
    "arv27:100": "Idam-avocad Bhagavān | āttamanāste bhikṣavaḥ sā ca sarvāvatī parṣat | sadeva-mānuṣāsura-gandharvaś-ca loko | Bhagavato bhāṣitam-abhyanandann-iti ||",
    "arv27:101": "Artha-Viniścaya-Dharma-Paryāyaḥ Samāptaḥ",
    "arv27:102": "Ye dharmā hetu-prabhavā, hetus-teṣāṁ Tathāgato hyavadat | Teṣāṁ ca yo nirodha—evaṁ-vādī mahā-śramaṇaḥ ||",
    "arv27:103": "Likhitam-Idaṁ Samvat 319 Caitra Śukla 9"
